**File:** loop.ipd

**Shows:** Loops, Iterating over XML nodes, building variables with multiple values in a loop.

**Components:** Start Element, Loop, Mapping Element, End Element, Connection

This process creates a simple XML document in the Start Element, iterates over the the nodes of the document, extracts the attribute "text" from each node and creates a variable containing all the values of the attributes as text. Each attribute value is logged within the Loop. The variable containing the values is passed out of the Loop and provided as output of the process.
